                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000219-85-off513 t18000219-85-cd514"></join>, a book, value 1s. two guineas, four half-guineas, a waistcoat, value 10s. 6d. a pair of breeches, value 15s. and a shirt, value 7s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18000219-85-victim782" type="victimName">
