                     <interp inst="t18000219-85-verdict517" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               Of stealing to the value of 39s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18000219-85-punish518" type="punishmentDescription">
